  "body": "Here is unlimited: https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/blob/6338bacc9553b7341268a386aa9093b59e2812f5/eth/stagedsync/stage_execute.go#L770\r\n\r\nReason is: stage LogIndex (Prune or Forward) does read everything what not pruned. Maybe need improve LogIndex - so it can take in account value of â€”prune flag, not just iterate over all logs/changesets which we have in DB. \r\n\r\nProblem: too long pruning, does stop node from sync. https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/issues/6564\r\n\r\nOpinion: \r\n- also can prune as much as possible if initialSync=true, otherwise prune by small steps (like 100 blocks limit, or 500ms limit). \r\n",
